To be fair, I cried when Harry Reid stepped down too. Tears of joy. 
On a serious note, I hate how Schumer constantly implies that his political opponents don’t care about immigrants. That’s not true. Asking them to come here legally is NOT hateful, and keeping terrorists out of this country isn’t anti-immigrant. It’s common sense.
